<p><a href="http://assets.runemadsen.com/function_engineering-ac37089eacf3de3d4ded586014fe2636_large.jpg"><img src="http://assets.runemadsen.com/function_engineering-ac37089eacf3de3d4ded586014fe2636_medium.jpg" srcset="http://assets.runemadsen.com/function_engineering-ac37089eacf3de3d4ded586014fe2636_medium.jpg 800w, http://assets.runemadsen.com/function_engineering-ac37089eacf3de3d4ded586014fe2636_large.jpg 1440w" sizes="600px" /></a></p>

